The '''Academy of Lightning''' is a building in the [[Elite Barracks]] category. It is used to recruit [[Lightning Mage]]s.

== Production ==
The Academy of Lightning produces one [[Lightning Mage]] every 25 seconds. It consumes 100 [[Wheat]] per cycle.

